<subsection xml:id="subsec-dot-product">
<title>Dot Product</title>
<paragraphs xml:id="para-dot-definition">
<title>Definition</title>
<p>The dot product between two vectors <m>\mathbf{a},\mathbf{b}\in \mathcal{V}_n</m> where <m>\mathcal{V_n} \sube \mathbb{R}^n </m> is given by:</p>
<me>\mathbf{a}\cdot\mathbf{b} = |a| |b| \cos{\theta} .</me>
<note>
<p>The dot product is the symmetric component of the geometric product.</p>
</note>
</paragraphs>
